      </odd>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_ef04a61af4f41ce78571feed6b70fde3">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The student records consist of transcripts, correspondence, and applications to the Committee on Honors and Academic Standing, which oversees the Special Divisional Major program.  A Special Divisional Major provides an alternative for students whose academic goals cannot be met by an existing department or special major.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
